a:5:{s:5:"title";s:40:"Attio adds associated notes in meetings";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:316:"<p>Attio introduced a notes section on meeting cards to surface linked notes without opening separate views. Notes indicators now also show up in meeting modals, ⌘K quick previews, and record activity timelines.</p>
